productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Georgie has one of these. She works as a busboy and she says it looks brown.
one of my hobbies is poetry. and when i'm writing poems this works great.
The box this comes in is 3 inch by 6 centimeter and weights 15 ounce!
It only works when I'm Chad.
My co-worker Rey has one of these. He says it looks uneven.
